    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface QueryExecutor<Result,Param>
    A generic extension to enable plugging into various searches.

    Consider extending QueryExecutorBase instead unless you know what you're doing.

    • Method Detail

      • execute

        boolean execute(Param queryParameters,
                Processor<? super Result> consumer)
        Find some results according to queryParameters and feed them to consumer. If consumer returns false, stop.
        Returns:
        false if the searching should be stopped immediately. This should happen only when consumer has returned false.
